{
  "stem": "25288.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you are, and your family, on this list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we decide-- decided that we leave the country.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, I was afraid of death, because it happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Things like this happened in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the second was, I didn't want my children grow up in a Communist country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then we decided that we going to leave Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Henry was eight, seven-- seven, eight years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Marta was six and a half.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did we have what?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it wasn't free [INAUDIBLE] religious in-- in Hungary, by the Communists.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if you was practice religious-- Jewish, or Catholic, or any kind of religious-- you might lose your job.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it wasn't [? wholly ?] religious.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to the temple every Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] when-- when I could go to the temple.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a-- first couple of years, I had my own business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then they come, and they took my business.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got a government-- a job at a government store.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I did-- didn't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I just was practicing for my-- my religion, how much I could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it wasn't free-- free religion, by the Communists.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People-- I'm not talking about Jewish people-- people who want to go to a church some day, they went on different [INAUDIBLE], and they went over there to-- to-- to the church.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because if they were watching people-- and when-- when they saw you go to the church Sunday, you might-- might lose your job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- we had a radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And the radio-- we heard in the radio, is a revolution broke out in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
